  "A qubit state is a unit vector in C^2, the 2-dimensional complex Hilbert space. The state |psi> = alpha|0> + beta|1> where |alpha|^2 + |beta|^2 = 1.": "",
  "The inner product <psi|phi> in quantum mechanics uses which type of inner product?": "",
