  "The inverse of the Hamiltonian": "",
  "A diagonal matrix of probabilities": "",
  "A density matrix rho is a positive semi-definite Hermitian matrix with trace(rho) = 1. For a pure state, rho = |psi><psi|. For mixed states (statistical ensembles), it generalizes the state vector description.": "",
